{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Handles push notification registration failure."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSError","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"error","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The NSError received from APNs registration failure","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"error"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Call this method from your AppDelegate’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"application:didFailToRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithError:"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to notify Pushwoosh about registration failures.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This allows Pushwoosh to:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Log the error for debugging"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Retry registration if appropriate"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Update device status in the Control Panel"}]}]}]},{"text":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle registration failure with user feedback:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class AppDelegate: UIResponder, UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func application(_ application: UIApplication,","                    didFailToRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithError error: Error) {","","        \/\/ Forward to Pushwoosh","        Pushwoosh.configure.handlePushRegistrationFailure(error as NSError)","","        \/\/ Log for debugging","        Logger.error(\"Push registration failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","","        \/\/ Handle specific error cases","        let nsError = error as NSError","        switch nsError.code {","        case 3010:","            \/\/ Simulator or push not supported","            Logger.warning(\"Push notifications not supported on this device\")","","        default:","            \/\/ Track error in analytics","            Analytics.track(\"push_registration_failed\", properties: [","                \"error_code\": nsError.code,","                \"error_message\": nsError.localizedDescription","            ])","","            \/\/ Optionally notify user","            if shouldShowPushError {","                showPushRegistrationError()","            }","        }","    }","}"]}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handlePushRegistrationFailure:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handlepushregistrationfailure:"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)handlePushRegistrationFailure:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","title":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","kind":"identifier"}]},"kind":